Bd6 (9... c4 $6 10. Qa4 $36 {[%cal Gf3e5,Gb2b3,Ge3e4]}) 10. dxc5 Bxc5 11. b3
O-O 12. Bb2 {[%csl Rc5,Rc6,Rc8][%cal Ga1c1] Black has the bishop pair and
