{[%cal Yh4g6,Yh4f5,Yh4f3] White doesn't rush capturing on g6 since his
h4-knight might be useful in some lines.} Rad8 18. Ne2 Ne4 19. Bg2 $14 {
[%cal Ge2d4,Yh4f5,Yh4g6]}) (14... Rc8 15. Nd4 $1 Nxd4 16. Bxh5 Ne6 $1 {[%cal
Ge6g5] The only way to avoid being clearly worse.} 17. Bf3 Be5 18. Rc1 Ng5 $1
19. Bg4 Rc6 20. Bf5 $1 $14 {[%csl Gf5] /=}) 15. Rc1 {is a semi-useful waiting
move. But it's hardly any stronger than the alternatives.} (15. Nh4 {is a
