Ra6,Yb2,Rc6,Yf3][%cal Gg2g3,Ga1c1,Gd1d3] 1-0 (35) Carlsen, M (2864)
-Praggnanandhaa,R (2624) Oslo 2022}) (12... Rc8 {is playable but a bit slow,
