cxb6 axb6 20. d5 $1 c5 21. Nb5 $18 {[%csl Ya6][%cal Gd5d6] 1-0 (31) Visakh,N (
2538) -Beisteiner,J (2055) Bad Woerishofen 2023}) 10. cxd5 $1 {[%cal Yc2c6]
