Nxd6 {It's logical to win the bishop pair while we can.} ({However, the
attacking option} 13. g4 $1 Ne8 14. f4 $16 {[%csl Gf5,Rg7] was even more
promising}) 13... Qxd6 14. d4 $14 {White has the upper hand thanks to the
