11. Nf3 $1 $146 O-O 12. Be2 $14 {[%cal Ge1g1,Rc6c5,Re7e5,Yf3g5]}) 9... Qxb3 10.
axb3 {[%csl Ya1][%cal Ga4b6,Yb3c4]} Nbd7 11. Nxd7 Nxd7 {[%cal Ra4b6,Ra4c5]
Black needs to play like this to prevent White's threats. But now we can
