Black improves his d7-knight and prepares the d5-retreat for the other one.}
10. Be2 Bd6 {This move looks less weakening for Black} ({than} 10... c5 11. Nf3
{[%cal Rb4d5,Gb4c6] Black removed the white knight from the strong central
